Content.title: Chris Houston
Content.name: Chris Houston
Content.bodyText:
Hi Darren,
Sounds like an interesting project. Are you looking at any sort of integration with Expression Media? (used to be a http://www.iview-multimedia.com/)

I've used it for years for cataloging my photos as have thousands of other photographers as it was the best too out there for a long time.

I am sure tight integration with Expression Media would be of great benefit to a lot of users who now use it.

Cheers,

Chris
